## Emerald Cut Diamond Hoop Earrings

If you want maximum diamond presence without the stud price, hoops are the answer.

The inside-out hoop style lines emerald cut stones along both the inside and outside of the hoop. At 3ct tw, you get far more visible diamond than a 1ct tw stud pair — and the [3ct tw white gold hoop currently costs $4,995](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/inside-out-emerald-cut-diamond-hoop-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-3-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251167?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) on sale from $6,660. That is $755 less than the prong stud at 1ct tw — while giving you three times the total diamond weight.

