## 1 Carat Emerald Cut Diamond Earrings

This is the most searched size. It is also the size where The Total Weight Trap catches the most buyers.

Read it clearly: **1 carat emerald cut diamond earrings = 1ct tw = 0.5ct per ear.** If you want one full carat per ear, you need 2ct tw. That costs [$13,190](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/emerald-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-2-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251836?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational).

