Buy the [bezel at $3,080](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/bezel-set-emerald-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251746?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Save $2,670. Or redirect that $2,670 toward the [3ct tw inside-out hoop at $4,995](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/inside-out-emerald-cut-diamond-hoop-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-3-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251167?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) instead.

