## FAQ

### What does "ct tw" mean on diamond earrings?

"Ct tw" means carat total weight — the combined weight of both earrings. A pair listed as 1ct tw contains two stones at 0.5ct each. If you want 1ct per ear, you need 2ct tw. In almost all earring listings, every carat weight shown is the total for the pair, not per stone.

### Are bezel set emerald cut diamond earrings better than prong set?

For the emerald cut specifically, yes. Bezel protects the flat corners, eliminates prong shadows on the open table, stays secure without tips to bend, and costs significantly less — [$3,080 vs $5,750 at 1ct tw](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/bezel-set-emerald-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251746?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). It is the better setting on every measure for this shape.

### How much do 1 carat emerald cut diamond earrings cost?

"1 carat emerald cut diamond earrings" almost always means 1ct tw — two 0.5ct stones. Bezel studs start at [$3,080 in 14K gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/bezel-set-emerald-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251746?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Prong studs cost [$5,750](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/emerald-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251830?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). If you want 1ct per ear (2ct tw), expect [$13,190](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/emerald-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-2-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251836?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational).

### What is the difference between 1ct and 1ct tw in diamond earrings?

1ct would mean a single stone weighing one carat. 1ct tw means both earrings combined weigh 1 carat — each holding a 0.5ct stone. In earring listings, you will almost always see the tw designation. If you want 1ct per ear, shop for 2ct tw pairs.

### Are emerald cut diamond studs good for everyday wear?

Yes — especially in bezel setting. The bezel protects the corners and keeps the stone secure through daily movement. In prong setting, the exposed corners and tip wire are more vulnerable to hair and fabric snagging. For daily wear, bezel is the practical choice on this shape.

### What is the best carat size for emerald cut stud earrings?

Most buyers find 1ct tw (0.5ct per ear) is the right balance of size and price. The emerald cut's rectangular face reads clearly and distinctly at that size without being heavy. The [bezel version at $3,080](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/bezel-set-emerald-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251746?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) makes that size genuinely accessible.

### What metal should I choose for emerald cut diamond earrings?

White gold and platinum show off the stone most cleanly. Yellow gold adds warmth and pairs naturally with the step-cut flashes. Pricing is identical for 14K white and yellow gold across all styles. Platinum carries a small premium. Choose by skin tone and your existing jewelry.

### What are inside-out emerald cut diamond hoop earrings?

Inside-out hoops set diamonds on both the inner and outer surfaces of the hoop — meaning the stones are visible from every angle, including from below. The emerald cut style lines rectangular stones along the full hoop for a continuous band of diamond presence. The [3ct tw white gold version is currently $4,995](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/inside-out-emerald-cut-diamond-hoop-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-3-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251167?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational).

### Can I get lab grown emerald cut diamond earrings?

Yes. Every product in this post offers a lab grown diamond option via the "+ Lab Grown" toggle on the product page. Lab grown diamonds are physically and chemically identical to natural. In earrings, where you are buying two stones at once, the savings are considerable — typically 60–70% less than the natural equivalent.

### What is the difference between emerald cut and round diamond stud earrings?

Round brilliant studs scatter light in all directions — high sparkle, soft circular outline. Emerald cut studs throw deliberate, long flashes of light — lower scatter, strong rectangular outline. The emerald cut reads as more modern and structured. It is a distinctive look that stands clearly apart from standard round studs.

### How do I choose between stud, hoop, and drop emerald cut earrings?

Start with occasion. Studs work everywhere. Hoops add presence and movement — suitable for daily wear and events. Drops are formal and occasion-specific. For most buyers, the [bezel stud at 1ct tw](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/bezel-set-emerald-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251746?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) or the [inside-out hoop at 3ct tw](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/inside-out-emerald-cut-diamond-hoop-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-3-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251167?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) covers the full range of daily and dressy wear.

### What clarity grade do I need for emerald cut diamond earrings?

The earrings in this post are graded H-I color and SI1-SI2 clarity as a set pair. For round cuts, SI2 is often clean to the eye because the faceting hides inclusions. The emerald cut's open step facets show more — inclusions are more visible. The pre-made pairs listed here have already been vetted at SI1-SI2. If you ever build a custom earring with loose stones, stay at VS2 or better in the emerald cut.

### Are emerald cut diamond earrings worth the price over other shapes?

If you like the rectangular step-cut look — yes. The emerald cut in earrings does something a round or cushion cannot: it gives you clean, linear flashes at ear level that read as a distinct, deliberate shape. At [1ct tw bezel starting at $3,080](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/bezel-set-emerald-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251746?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational), the price is genuinely accessible for what the shape delivers.

